[tcell_events://<name>]
tcell_company_name = If your tCell domain is widgets.tcell.io, enter widgets here.
tcell_api_key = tCell account API key. Generate one from the tCell api: "Logged in as <Your Name>" ->  Account Settings -> API Keys -> create Read-Only API key.
tcell_app_id = Find your tCell App ID under Admin -> Applications  in the "Application ID" column.  The App ID is also the segment of the url used when viewing a particular app in the tCell web UI.
tcell_apps = Select this option to collect data for all apps.
appsensor = Suspicious behavior by requests against the app
vulnerabilities = Vulnerabilities in packages and libraries used within the app
packages = Packages and libraries used within the app
login = Unusual login behavior information
inline = Unexpected inline scripts detected by the jsagent within the users' browsers.
csp = Content Security Policy violation information reported by user browsers
cmdi = Unusual, unallowed shell command
lfi = A malicious local file included or imported in the app